</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1035,654,705]" pageId="10" pageNumber="969">
E t y m o l o g y: Thetrivialname, 
<emphasis box="[537,592,655,676]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="969">arsus</emphasis>
, is a Latin adjective from 
<emphasis box="[859,907,654,675]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="969">ardo</emphasis>
(= glow); in reference to the bluish tinge on the elytral disc.
</paragraph>
